    "id": "ann_mmp85oz4_fw9n",
    "title": "The Dawn of a New Era",
    "body": "<div style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size: 0.82rem; letter-spacing: 0.02em;\">To the Owners, Managers, and Bracket-Busters of the Realm, i</span><span style=\"font-size: 0.85rem; letter-spacing: 0.02em;\">t is my distinct honor to announce the formal ratification of the </span><b data-path-to-node=\"6\" data-index-in-node=\"67\" style=\"font-size: 0.85rem; letter-spacing: 0.02em;\">Osborne Fantasy League (OFL)</b><span style=\"font-size: 0.85rem; letter-spacing: 0.02em;\">.</span></div><p data-path-to-node=\"6\"><br></p><p data-path-to-node=\"7\">For years, we have battled across gridirons and hardwoods in isolated skirmishes. Today, those efforts are unified. The OFL now serves as the governing body for both the <b data-path-to-node=\"7\" data-index-in-node=\"170\">OFC (Football)</b> and the <b data-path-to-node=\"7\" data-index-in-node=\"193\">BRC (Basketball)</b>, bringing our storied history and future ambitions under one digital roof.</p><p data-path-to-node=\"7\"><span style=\"font-size: large; letter-spacing: 0.02em; text-align: center;\"><br></span></p><p data-path-to-node=\"7\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: large; letter-spacing: 0.02em; text-align: center;\">What Awaits You:</span></p><ul data-path-to-node=\"9\"><li><p data-path-to-node=\"9,0,0\">The Playas: putting a face to the pain</p></li><li><p data-path-to-node=\"9,3,0\"><b data-path-to-node=\"9,3,0\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Standings:</b>&nbsp;dedicated to determining the truth</p></li><li><p data-path-to-node=\"9,0,0\">OFC/BRC: the birthplace of bragging rights</p></li><li><p data-path-to-node=\"9,0,0\">Trophy Case: the gifts to greatness</p></li><li><b data-path-to-node=\"9,1,0\" data-index-in-node=\"0\" style=\"font-size: 0.85rem; letter-spacing: 0.02em;\">Hall of Records:</b><span style=\"font-size: 0.85rem; letter-spacing: 0.02em;\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-size: 0.85rem; letter-spacing: 0.02em;\">where warriors are immortalized</span></li></ul><div><b data-path-to-node=\"11\" data-index-in-node=\"0\" style=\"text-align: center; font-size: 0.82rem; letter-spacing: 0.02em;\"><br></b></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><b data-path-to-node=\"11\" data-index-in-node=\"0\" style=\"text-align: center; font-size: 0.82rem; letter-spacing: 0.02em;\">Go forth, and bask in the light.</b></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span data-path-to-node=\"11\" data-index-in-node=\"0\" style=\"text-align: center; letter-spacing: 0.02em;\"><font size=\"5\"><b>Welcome to the OFL</b></font></span></div>",
